    <h1 class="gem-c-title__text govuk-heading-l">
      Update your registration of interest
    </h1>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Please give us some more information to make it easier for local councils and other organisations to match your offer with people coming to the UK.</p>

    <h1 class="gem-c-title__text govuk-heading-l">
      Before you start
    </h1>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph"><%= govuk_link_to "Read the guidance", "https://www.gov.uk/guidance/homes-for-ukraine-scheme-frequently-asked-questions" %> about the Homes for Ukraine scheme and make sure you understand what a big commitment becoming a sponsor is.</p>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Have a discussion with everyone in your household about how sharing your home with people fleeing Ukraine may affect your lives.</p>

    <%= govuk_button_link_to "Start", "/additional-info/start/#{params["reference"]}" %>
  </div>
</div>

